Options:

&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;-r &amp;lt;lines&amp;gt;: Specify lines or ranges of lines to load from the source.  
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Ranges could be specified as x-y (x..y) or in python-style x:y
